title: #92Noon Live from TCO: Wobby / Warren / Caplan / Birk / Eskin
description: The October 3rd edition of 9-To-Noon is live from the TCO Performance Center in Eagan, and welcomes Vikings.com's Mike Wobschall, Vikings COO Kevin Warren, NFL insider Adam Caplan, Super Bowl champion Matt Birk, and Fox29 Philadelphia's Howard Eskin to the program.
